content: Agents can use the PharmacyBenefitsVerification FlexCard to record responses from payers about verification requests. This applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Health Cloud or Life Sciences Cloud license, starting June 2024. The feature is available to users with Health Cloud Foundation (for Health Cloud) or Health Cloud Starter (for Life Sciences Cloud), and Manage Pharmacy Benefits Verification permission set. Add the flexcard to the Care Program Enrollee record page.
title: Record Responses from Payers
